                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "Your team's AI assistant — trained on your documents, products, and customer history. Running entirely on your infrastructure.\n\nPick a specialized agent, attach files, and get answers grounded in your company's actual data. No data leaves your servers.",
