                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "Every customer channel in one inbox — with AI that actually knows your business. Responses drafted by models running on your servers.\n\nRoute conversations to the right team automatically. AI suggests replies from your knowledge base, past tickets, and product data.",
